type.name: org.gradle.tooling.events.OperationResult
type.description:
Describes the result of running an operation.
(since 2.4)

method.name: getEndTime
method.description:
Returns the time when the operation finished its execution.

returns:The end time, in milliseconds since the epoch.

method.name: getStartTime
method.description:
Returns the time when the operation started its execution.

returns:The start time, in milliseconds since the epoch.

property.name: endTime
property.description:
Returns the time when the operation finished its execution.

returns:The end time, in milliseconds since the epoch.

property.name: startTime
property.description:
Returns the time when the operation started its execution.

returns:The start time, in milliseconds since the epoch.
